  "texts": [
    "If the statement does not contain a specific service name, generate an appropriate string that succinctly represents the service as the service name.\"",
    "Second, the keyword extraction API processes 6W1H needs and outputs three representative keywords for the service.",
    "If extraction fails, it returns an empty list.",
    "The prompt included the instruction: \"Extract three representative noun keywords that describe the service, following this user need definition in JSON.\"",
    "Lastly, the upcycling case retrieval API uses the extracted 6W1H needs to search the SUCCEED system, obtaining relevant upcycling cases by first calling the keyword extraction API, then executing the SUCCEED search API to return cases.This section discusses the computational resources and hardware requirements necessary to implement the proposed method."
  ]
